<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify your email – NextVIP</title>
    <!--[if mso]>
    <noscript>
      <xml>
        <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
          <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
        </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
      </xml>
    </noscript>
    <![endif]-->
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100vw;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #0f172a;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #ffffff 50%, #f5f3ff 100%);
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      }
      .preheader {
        display: none;
        max-height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .email-root {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        padding: 40px 24px;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 20px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.9);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08);
      }
      .brand {
        width: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #4f46e5 100%);
        padding: 36px 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .brand-inner {
        display: inline-block;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .brand-row {
        display: table;
        border-collapse: collapse;
      }
      .brand-icon-cell {
        display: table-cell;
        vertical-align: middle;
        padding-right: 12px;
      }
      .brand-icon {
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22);
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 44px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .brand-text-cell {
        display: table-cell;
        vertical-align: middle;
      }
      .brand-name {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        color: #ffffff;
        line-height: 1.1;
      }
      .brand-name span {
        color: #ddd6fe;
      }
      .brand-tagline {
        margin: 4px 0 0;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      .main {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 40px 32px 32px;
      }
      .icon-badge {
        width: 56px;
        height: 56px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        background: #ede9fe;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 56px;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .title {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #0f172a;
        text-align: center;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      .subtitle {
        margin: 0 0 28px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #64748b;
        line-height: 1.65;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .greeting {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #0f172a;
      }
      .intro {
        margin: 0 0 28px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #475569;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }
      .code-label {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #64748b;
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      }
      .code-block {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f3ff 0%, #eef2ff 100%);
        border: 1px solid #ddd6fe;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px 16px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 0 20px;
      }
      .code-value {
        display: inline-block;
        max-width: 100%;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 10px;
        color: #7c3aed;
        font-family: 'SF Mono', Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      .code-actions {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 0 24px;
      }
      .copy-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #4f46e5 100%);
        color: #ffffff;
        border: none;
        padding: 12px 28px;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-family: inherit;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.25);
      }
      .expiry {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #64748b;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background-color: #e2e8f0;
        margin: 28px 0 24px;
      }
      .disclaimer {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #64748b;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .sign-off {
        margin: 24px 0 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #0f172a;
      }
      .footer-wrap {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 24px 32px 32px;
        background: #f8fafc;
        border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }
      .footer-text {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #94a3b8;
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <span class="preheader">Your NextVIP verification code is <%= verificationCode %>. Use it to activate your account.</span>
    <div class="email-root">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="brand">
            <div class="brand-inner">
              <div class="brand-row">
                <div class="brand-icon-cell">
                  <div class="brand-icon">N</div>
                </div>
                <div class="brand-text-cell">
                  <h1 class="brand-name">Next<span>VIP</span></h1>
                  <p class="brand-tagline">Content automation SaaS</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="main">
            <div class="icon-badge">✉️</div>
            <h2 class="title">Verify your email</h2>
            <p class="subtitle">Enter this code on the verification screen to activate your account.</p>

            <p class="greeting">Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p class="intro">
              Thanks for signing up for NextVIP. Use the 6-digit code below to complete your registration and start publishing across TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, and YouTube.
            </p>

            <p class="code-label">Verification code</p>
            <div class="code-block">
              <span class="code-value" id="verification-code"><%= verificationCode %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="code-actions">
              <button type="button" class="copy-btn" id="copy-code-btn" onclick="var el=document.getElementById('verification-code'); var code=el?el.textContent.trim():''; if(code && navigator.clipboard){navigator.clipboard.writeText(code).then(function(){var b=document.getElementById('copy-code-btn');if(b){b.textContent='Copied!';setTimeout(function(){b.textContent='Copy code';},2000);}});} return false;">Copy code</button>
            </div>
            <p class="expiry">
              This code expires in <%= expiresInMinutes %> minutes. Do not share it with anyone.
            </p>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <p class="disclaimer">
              If you did not create an account with NextVIP, you can safely ignore this email.
            </p>
            <p class="sign-off">Best regards,<br />The NextVIP Team</p>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-wrap">
            <p class="footer-text">
              You received this message because an account was created with this email address.<br />
              NextVIP – Content automation SaaS
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
